<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Cross-Chain - 标签 - Lucas's Blog</title><link>https://lucas5.xyz/tags/cross-chain/</link><description>一个专注于区块链安全/密码学和开发工具的技术博客. | A technical blog focused on blockchain security, cryptography, and developer tools.</description><generator>Hugo 0.147.7 &amp; FixIt v0.4.0-alpha-20250721024521-a1cd700b</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://lucas5.xyz/tags/cross-chain/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>基于区块链交易公钥在多链进行跨链追查：原理与实践</title><link>https://lucas5.xyz/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%9D%97%E9%93%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%85%AC%E9%92%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%9A%E9%93%BE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%A8%E9%93%BE%E8%BF%BD%E6%9F%A5%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://lucas5.xyz/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%9D%97%E9%93%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%85%AC%E9%92%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%9A%E9%93%BE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%A8%E9%93%BE%E8%BF%BD%E6%9F%A5%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</guid><category domain="https://lucas5.xyz/categories/blockchain/">Blockchain</category><category domain="https://lucas5.xyz/categories/multi-chain/">Multi-Chain</category><category domain="https://lucas5.xyz/categories/security/">Security</category><description>&lt;p>随着区块链技术的不断发展,越来越多的项目和资金分散在不同的区块链网络中.对于合规审计、安全追踪和资金流动分析等场景,如何确定同一个私钥是否在多条链上产生实际交易,往往是突破口之一.本文将介绍一个&lt;strong>普适的技术思路&lt;/strong>：通过在某条链(如以太坊)获取交易公钥,再将其转换到另一条采用相同椭圆曲线(secp256k1)的链(如比特币),进而在该链上验证是否有对应的签名交易,从而确认是否确系同一私钥所控.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>